        AdminCatalog updateCatalog(URI catalogRef,
                         AdminCatalog catalog)
        Modifies a catalog. A catalog could be published or unpublished. The IsPublished property is treated as a read only value by the server. In order to control publishing settings use the 'publish' action must be used. 
         PUT /admin/catalog/{id}
        Returns:
        the updated catalog
